{
  "stem": "7781.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But otherwise in Poland, you know, where we lived, we were quite, you know, content, and-- because of the family life, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had each other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You said that the kids always had trouble getting along with each other in school, or after school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the kids.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The kids-- if it come to Polish kids, and the Jewish kids--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--there was anti-semitism.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was-- they were aggressive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to beat us up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But between the Jewish kids, there was no problem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was-- I was interested in between the Jewish kids and the Polish kids.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We would-- we never-- we didn't mix.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we-- as the Jewish kids, we tried to stay away from them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- not-- not really friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we-- we had in the same-- in the same house, the families, the Polish kids lived there, but we had no problems with them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You lived it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- was getting--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--as the German-- as Hitler got more popular, more powerful, the Pollacks imitated him, you know, with the laws, and you could feel it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the press was there-- the press was more [? fashioned ?] after the after German hate paper.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- in the stores they put up-- Polish stores-- Christian enterprise, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the Polish shouldn't walk in the Jewish store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could feel it everywhere, you know, the hate, you know, against the Jewish people, that we weren't liked, would be putting it mildly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we had papers, and books, and--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I read.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew what was going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew about the concentration camps, and so forth, and all the-- the and the-- and the hate and the propaganda.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
